{"tid":1127363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★江郎才盡！Apple 大倒退？新 iPad Pro 或支援滑鼠操作！","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T05:43:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8d32bf69e6df79ab65d721a1c4b8365ec21adbb7","tid":1127363,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"Apple 一直以辦公工具深入人心，特別是在 MacBook 或者 iMac 產品上得到完美展現。而在近年，Apple 為了提升 iPad Pro 相對薄弱的辦公性能上花了心思去升級，但還是缺少些什麼，其中的一個難題可能就是滑鼠操控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時 iPad 已經增加了 Smart Keyboard、Apple Pencil 等支援，可以極大的提高iPad 的生產力。而根據外媒的爆料，Apple 或許將在後續為 iPad Pro 新增支援滑鼠「即插即用」功能，而且為此將會在最新一代 iPad Pro 上罕見地將 Lightning 接口改為 Type C 接口，目的就是為了能更好的兼容 USB 滑鼠等外設。<br />\n<br />\n對於該消息是否屬實，Apple 最快會於今年六月的 WWDC 開發者大會上介紹 iOS 13 時宣布此功能。<br />\n如果 Apple 真的加入了這個新功能，有了滑鼠功能的 iPad，相信會為一些習慣了鼠標操控的用戶帶了便利，讓辦公效率極大的提升。只是，這樣做的話就會失去了當初設計 iPad，作為一部可以取代輕量型手提電腦的目標，產品市場策略上確有大倒退的嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/04/26/ipad-pro-usb-mouse-support/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2Fipad-pro-usb-mouse-support%2F&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=ef06122d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/04/26/ipad-pro-usb-mouse-support/</a>"},{"pid":"ad8620e2a24d43cbc9f475231dbf69f1cc231b12","tid":1127363,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af13f23aa9072a8a6e8dba340e4601702dda4d8","tid":1127363,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad8620e2a24d43cbc9f475231dbf69f1cc231b12","tid":1127363,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係一部行ios 嘅noteb